videos.description: Jarron Cumberland catches a pass in the corner and pulls up to bury a 3-pointer and give Cincinnati the lead over UCF.
videos.headline: Cumberland drains corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Jarron Cumberland drives and puts up a floater, but 7-foot-6 Tacko Fall gets a hand on it for the block.

videos.headline: Fall blocks floater in the paint

videos.description: UCF guard Terrell Allen tosses an alley-oop pass to Chad Brown, who posterizes his defender with a vicious slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UCF's Brown hammers down poster dunk) 2019/2/21 ESHEET
